This program manages a fleet of vehicles for a delivery company.
Base Class: Vehicle
Attributes: make, model, year

The subclasses are:
    Car: Adds num_doors
    Truck: Adds payload_capacity

Extra functionality:
    Both should have a vehicle_info() method that prints details.
    Truck has an extra method load_cargo(weight) to load cargo if itâ€™s within capacity.

